All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
AllDistrictGen
Generator of all possible districts within a region.
District
A district is a contiguous group of locations.
Location
A distinguished location.
Party
Enumeration class Party specifies constants for all known parties as well as for unaffiliated and none (unknown).
Redistrictor
A redistrictor attempts to determine a set of districts for a given region under specified constraints.
Region
A region represents a politically-defined area comprised of locations and voters that occupy those locations.
Renderer
Utility class for rendering regions and districts.
SnakingLocationComparer
Snaking Location will compare locations in a snaking fashion meaning if all locations are in a grid any sequential block of locations read will be contiguous.
StarGenerator
Generates a list of possible districts of a specified size originating from an given origin point.
Voter
A voter has a party association and a location.
